Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Erica in a viral video, exposed her naked buttocks on national television for Kiddwaya. The incident happened after they had a private conversation. In the video, Erica, who was walking to the room, carried her dress up and exposed her naked body part to her lover. This is the first time a housemate will intentionally expose her body parts to the cameras on national tv. Recall that Erica on Wednesday confirmed she had sex and everything intimate with Kiddwaya. Meanwhile, Kiddwaya has said he cannot have a relationship with Erica outside the house yet because he is still working on himself and trying to be independent.